text: State Route 53 (SR 53) is a state highway in the U.S. state of Georgia. The highway's west end is at U.S. Route 411 (US 411) and Alabama State Route 25 at the Alabama state line near Cave Spring. Its east end is at US 129 Bus./US 441 Bus./SR 15/SR 24 Bus. in Watkinsville. The highway is long. ==References== Category:Roads in the United States Category:Transport in Georgia (U.S. state)
title: Georgia State Route 53
